vibrant culture.

132
00:08:01,291 --> 00:08:03,291
No, no! Why you...

133
00:08:03,375 --> 00:08:07,035
Oh, you rotten vermin!

134
00:08:37,291 --> 00:08:38,461
Where is everyone?

135
00:08:38,541 --> 00:08:39,541
Everyone?

136
00:08:39,625 --> 00:08:42,375
